y Review与大多数团队迁至美国华盛顿州的西雅图<ref>{{cite web|title=New beginners' guides and Site news: Digital Photography Review|url=http://www.dpreview.com/news/2010/10/20/sitenews|accessdate=2013-03-27|date=|publisher=Digital Photography Review|archive-date=2013-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511034118/http://www.dpreview.com/news/2010/10/20/sitenews|dead-url=no}}</ref>。目前此网站归属[[亚马逊公司|亚马逊公司]]<ref name="guardian-schofield-2009" /><ref>{{cite news|first1=Jack|last1=Schofield|accessdate=2019-08-19|title=Wanted: a travellers' compact camera with a long zoom lens|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/askjack/2011/aug/05/travel-compact-camera-zoom-lens|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2011-08-05|issn=0261-3077|via=www.theguardian.com|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729204037/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/askjack/2011/aug/05/travel-compact-camera-zoom-lens|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 主要特点 ==
自1998年该网站上线以来，DPReview定期发布详尽的<ref name="guardian-schofield-2009" /><ref name="wired" /><ref name="dummies">{{cite web|title=The Digital Photography Review|url=https://www.dummies.com/photography/photo-software/the-digital-photography-review/|accessdate=2019-08-19|website={{tsl|en|For Dummies||For Dummies}}|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729214915/https://www.dummies.com/photography/photo-software/the-digital-photography-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，针对技术的相机评测<ref name="theregister">{{cite web|title=Amazon.com snaps up Dpreview.com|url=https://www.theregister.co.uk/2007/05/15/amazon_buys_dpreview/|accessdate=2019-08-19|first1=John Leyden 15 May 2007|last1=at 13:07|website=www.theregister.co.uk|archive-date=2019-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190819093317/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2007/05/15/amazon_buys_dpreview/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="techcrunch">{{cite web|title=Amazon Acquires dpreview.com|url=http://social.techcrunch.com/2007/05/14/amazon-acquires-dpreviewcom/|accessdate=2019-08-19|website=TechCrunch}}</ref>。评论的深度与广度随时间变化，但是基本的测评流程（对操作和菜单的详尽描述，一贯不变可复现的摄影棚测试，像素级并列比较）自成立以来一直没有变。2004年，DPReview针对便携相机引入了一种较短的“简洁”评论格式<ref>{{cite web|title=Just posted! HP PhotoSmart R707 review: Digital Photography Review|url=http://www.dpreview.com/news/2004/08/13/hpr707review|accessdate=2013-03-27|date=|publisher=Digital Photography Review|archive-date=2014-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607150858/http://www.dpreview.com/news/2004/08/13/hpr707review|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并在2008年引入了分组测试<ref>{{cite web|title=Budget Compact Camera Group Test: Digital Photography Review|url=http://www.dpreview.com/news/2008/11/27/q408compactroundup1|accessdate=2013-03-27|date=|publisher=Digital Photography Review|archive-date=2014-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219134132/http://www.dpreview.com/news/2008/11/27/q408compactroundup1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该网站的相机评测始终提供与同类竞品相机并排对比的拍摄样张和测试结果<ref name="guardian-schofield-2009" />。2010年，网站引入了一个交互式比较小部件，使读者可以比较数据库中任一相机的摄影棚测评结论<ref>{{cite web|title=Studio comparison widget|url=http://www.dpreview.com/articles/2087305746/studio-comparison-widget|publisher=Digital Photography Review|accessdate=2020-11-30|archive-date=2020-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802150718/https://www.dpreview.com/articles/2087305746/studio-comparison-widget|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 之后的小部件增加了对比相机其他测试结果（例如噪点和动态范围）的功能。网站还提供了大规模的实际拍摄样片相册，包含所有评测过以及没有评测过的相机与镜头。

直到2010年2月，DPReview都没有对相机评过数字分数，而是使用了经常引起争议的<ref name="DPReview-scoring">{{cite web|title=DPReview Scoring Method|url=http://brainfunkers.co/blog/Digital-Photography-Review-Scoring-Method.html|accessdate=2020-01-06|website=brainfunkers.co|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925172715/https://brainfunkers.co/blog/Digital-Photography-Review-Scoring-Method.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>六级评分系统（按优劣依次为：强烈推荐，推荐，高于平均水平，平均，低于平均水平，较差）。 该网站现在使用多达11个分类对所有相机和镜头进行评分（这些分类又基于“相机性能和规格的近60个方面”构成）<ref>{{cite web|title=Camera Scores & Ratings Explained: Digital Photography Review|url=http://www.dpreview.com/learn/?/Guides/dpreview_scores_and_ratings_01.htm|accessdate=2013-03-27|author=Featured articles|date=2013-01-28|publisher=Digital Photography Review|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926082157/https://www.dpreview.com/learn/?%2FGuides%2Fdpreview_scores_and_ratings_01.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。与此同时新的计分系统引入了两个自由裁量奖（“金奖”和“银奖”）。

2008年，DPReview 推出了镜头测评栏目。<ref>{{cite web|title=Dpreview launches lens reviews: Digital Photography Review|url=http://www.dpreview.com/news/2008/01/29/dpreviewlensreviews|accessdate=2013-03-27|date=|publisher=Digital Photography Review|archive-date=2013-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510110623/http://www.dpreview.com/news/2008/01/29/dpreviewlensreviews|dead-url=no}}</ref>

尽管其大部分已发表的评论均与数码相机相关，但DPReview也会偶尔发布打印机，软件，摄影书，配件和移动成像设备的测评。

DPReview网站里设有一个数码相机，镜头，打印机和桌面成像软件包的数据库。 相机产品页面包含完整规格，产品和样本照片，用户评论<ref name="guardian-schofield-2009" />以及其他内部和外部资源的链接。 产品数据库具有浏览，搜索和比较同类产品的功能<ref>{{cite news|first1=Jack|last1=Schofield|accessdate=2019-08-19|title=Is there a camera that can produce high-quality still images from videos?|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/askjack/2017/aug/03/is-there-a-camera-that-can-produce-high-quality-still-images-from-videos|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2017-08-03|issn=0261-3077|via=www.theguardian.com|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111234753/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/askjack/2017/aug/03/is-there-a-camera-that-can-produce-high-quality-still-images-from-videos|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first1=Jack|last1=Schofield|accessdate=2019-08-19|title=What's the best cheap compact camera with image stabilisation?|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/askjack/2017/oct/19/best-cheap-compact-camera-image-stabiliser-sony-rx100|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2017-10-19|issn=0261-3077|via=www.theguardian.com|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112025604/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/askjack/2017/oct/19/best-cheap-compact-camera-image-stabiliser-sony-rx100|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first1=Jack|last1=Schofield|accessdate=2019-08-19|title=Which pocket camera should I buy for holidays?|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/askjack/2013/nov/14/camera-compact-canon-panasonic-samsung|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2013-11-14|issn=0261-3077|via=www.theguardian.com|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729210937/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/askjack/2013/nov/14/camera-compact-canon-panasonic-samsung|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

DPReview站内设有交流论坛<ref name="theregister" />，并参与评论<ref name="guardian-schofield-2009" />（针对某些但不是所有类型的内容），登载用户创建的文章和产品评论，提供摄影挑战与免费的个人画廊。网站向注册用户提供简易的个人消息系统。

DPReview偶尔会发表非测评文章，内容涉及影像科学与技术<ref name="theregister" /><ref name="dummies" />，摄影技术，采访摄影师和行业人物，以及购买指南<ref name="guardian-schofield-2009" />。 在2012年，DPReview增设了“链接目录”功能，这个功能允许注册用户查看和订阅DPReview网站外的[[RSS|RSS]]和[[推特|推特]]更新，而无需离开站点。

DPReview暂时没有在大中华区运营的计划，也没有中文内容，而与之相似的同类型测评网站[[DXOMARK|DxoMark]]则在2017年宣布提供中文版网站，并开始进入大中华区市场，针对手机提供测评服务<ref>{{Cite web|title=DxOMark 上线中文版！测评标准详情释出 - 相机 - IT之家|url=https://www.ithome.com/html/it/331728.htm|accessdate=2020-11-30|work=www.ithome.com}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=DxOMark镜头和传感器：中文版上线！|url=https://www.dxomark.cn/dxomark-lens-and-sensor-now-available-in-chinese/|accessdate=|author=Lars Rehm|date=2019-06-14|format=|publisher=www.dxomark.cn|language=|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216150000/https://www.dxomark.cn/dxomark-lens-and-sensor-now-available-in-chinese/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 所有权历史 ==
Philip和Joanna Askey夫妇于1998年12月在[[英国|英国]]成立了Digital Photography Review<ref name="guardian-schofield-2009" /><ref name="techcrunch" />。 2007年5月14日，网站被亚马逊收购<ref>{{cite web|title=DPreview Bought Out by Amazon: How Does This Affect You?|url=https://gizmodo.com/dpreview-bought-out-by-amazon-how-does-this-affect-you-260397|accessdate=2019-08-19|first1=Jason|last1=Chen|website=Gizmodo|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927115402/https://gizmodo.com/dpreview-bought-out-by-amazon-how-does-this-affect-you-260397|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="guardian-schofield-2009" /><ref name="wired" /> 。DPReview雇用了由内部和自由作家，组成专门的编辑团队，并且在编写评测时独立于亚马逊<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.dpreview.com/about |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-11-30 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201143130/https://www.dpreview.com/about |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

最初的创始人Phil Askey不再参与该站点的日常运行<ref name="about">{{cite web|title=Digital Photography Review - About Us|url=http://www.dpreview.com/misc/about.asp|accessdate=2013-03-27|date=2007-10-30|publisher=Digital Photography Review|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729211307/http://www.dpreview.com/misc/about.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 该公司直接雇用14名全职职工<ref name="about" />。 Askey卸任后由Simon Simonson担任总经理，他于2010年就任该职位。Joinson于2004年加入公司，此前曾创办和编辑过数本英国数码摄影杂志，包括What Digital Camera。

现任经理是Scott Everett，他于2011年以产品经理的身份加入DPReview。

2007年，该网站每月的独立访客突破了700万（“in excess of 7 million unique viewers monthly”）<ref name="techcrunch" />。

